sequenceDiagram
    title 后端异常消息修复后流程 (T02)

    participant C as Controller
    participant S as Service
    participant P as PrismaService
    participant OH as OwnershipHelper

    C->>S: findById(id, userId)
    S->>P: findUnique({ where: { id } })
    P-->>S: null
    S-->>C: throw NotFoundException('内容不存在: id=' + id)

    C->>S: create(dto, userId)
    S->>P: findUnique(account)
    P-->>S: { id, userId: 'other' }
    S->>OH: assertOwnershipOrAdmin(userId, 'other', prisma, '账号')
    OH->>P: findUnique(user)
    P-->>OH: { role: 'MEMBER' }
    OH-->>S: throw ForbiddenException('无权操作该账号')

---

sequenceDiagram
    title 前端发布重试流程 (T03+T04)

    participant V as PublishView
    participant API as contentApi
    participant B as Backend

    V->>V: publishing = true
    V->>API: publish({...accountIds})
    API->>B: POST /api/v1/content/batch-publish
    B-->>API: { success, posts, failedIds? }

    alt 全部成功
        API-->>V: { success: true }
        V->>V: ElMessage.success('发布完成')
    else 部分失败
        API-->>V: { success: false, failedIds: [...] }
        V->>V: ElMessage.warning('N 个账号失败')
        V->>V: showRetryButton = true
    end

    Note over V: publishing = false (finally)

    opt 用户点击重试
        V->>API: retryPublish({ failedAccountIds })
        API->>B: POST /api/v1/content/batch-publish
        B-->>API: results
        API-->>V: results
    end

---

sequenceDiagram
    title 桌面端认证流程 (T05)

    participant F as Frontend
    participant SB as sau_backend.py
    participant PW as Playwright
    participant C as Cloud API

    F->>SB: GET /api/scan-bind/start?token=JWT&platform=douyin
    SB->>SB: verify_token(token)

    alt Token 无效
        SB-->>F: 401 {"code":401,"msg":"未授权"}
    else Token 有效
        SB->>PW: 启动浏览器扫码登录
        PW-->>SB: QR URL
        SB-->>F: SSE: {type:"qr_code", data:"..."}
        PW-->>SB: 200 (扫码成功)
        SB-->>F: SSE: {type:"status", data:"扫码成功，正在上传..."}
        SB->>C: POST /accounts (Bearer JWT)
        C-->>SB: { account }
        SB-->>F: SSE: {type:"success", data:{...}}
    end

---

sequenceDiagram
    title chrome_mgr CDP WebSocket 流程 (T05)

    participant Caller
    participant CM as ChromeManager
    participant WS as WebSocket Client
    participant CDP as Chrome DevTools

    Caller->>CM: evaluate(page_id, "document.title")
    CM->>CM: get_pages() → find webSocketDebuggerUrl
    CM->>WS: connect(ws_url)
    WS->>CDP: {"id":1, "method":"Runtime.evaluate", "params":{...}}
    CDP-->>WS: {"id":1, "result":{...}}
    WS-->>CM: result value
    CM-->>Caller: "页面标题"

    Note over CM: 替代原来的 HTTP urllib 请求
